| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7133 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6554c077-b4b8-5bfe-9075-8d05cef1bbd2"
